  "title": "Production Supervisor (Precision) (Up to $4000)",
  "description": "<p>Production Supervisor<br>\nBasic Salary : $2600-$3500</p>\n<p>Gross Salary : $3500-$4000++<br>\nMon-Fri 8am-5.30pm, Sat 8am-12pm (Alt)<br>\nSun &amp; PH off<br>\nLocation at Loyang</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>-Bonus<br>\n-After confirmation increment<br>\n-Yearly increment<br>\n-8 days annual leave (Max 14 days)<br>\n-Medical benefits</p>\n<p><strong>Authorities and Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>To organize, co-ordinate, check and ensure all production      activities follow as plan.</li>\n  <li>Calculate machine cycle time and organize production schedule      base on machine capacity and capabilities</li>\n  <li>Plan manpower resources and delegate machining job to machinist</li>\n  <li>Verify program issue to workshop</li>\n  <li>Analyze and provide solution to solve problems between      programmer and production dept.</li>\n  <li>Analyze monthly machining and scrap report</li>\n  <li>Good supervisory skill, people skill and 5 ‘S’ housekeeping</li>\n  <li>Good writing and communicating skill</li>\n  <li>Good in mechanical process, such as machining process, H/T, jig      and fixture etc.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Competence Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preferred NTC 2 / Diploma in Engineering discipline or      equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of working in related industry, and having 2 –      3 years of supervisory experience and preferably with working knowledge in      machining processes.</li>\n  <li>PC literate</li>\n  <li>Possess excellent interpersonal communication skills and is an      effective team player who is also self driven with a strong achievement      orientation.</li>\n</ul>",
